fields.title: Creation of a TG Bot
fields.description: Creating a Telegram bot is the task of developing a software agent capable of interacting with users through the Telegram platform. A bot can perform various functions: from providing information and answering questions to automating certain tasks. To implement this task, the use of programming and the Telegram API is required, as well as defining the functionality that the bot will provide to its users.

fields.title: Playing guitar
fields.description: Guitar playing is a creative and musical endeavor that involves using the guitar to play melodies, chords, or solos. As part of this task, the musician can work on learning new compositions, creating his own arrangements, and honing his playing technique. This requires not only musical skills, but also the ability to read music, analyze chords and think creatively to personalize the performance.

fields.title: Physical state
fields.description: The task of assessing a person's physical condition involves analyzing and measuring various parameters related to physical health. This may include measuring heart rate, blood pressure, analyzing physical activity levels, physical endurance levels and other metrics. The goal may also include developing and implementing physical activity, nutrition, or rehabilitation programs to improve the overall physical condition of the individual.

fields.title: Find a job
fields.description: The job search task includes researching job openings, analyzing employer requirements, and preparing a resume. It also includes active participation in the employment process, including directed searches, participation in interviews and development of professional skills. An effective job search requires a strategic approach, self-promotion and the ability to present your qualities and skills to employers.

fields.title: New Year
fields.description: Preparing for the New Year is a task associated with creating a festive atmosphere and planning events for the transition to a new calendar year. Includes decorating the house, choosing gifts for loved ones, creating a holiday menu, planning meetings and events. Organization of festive mood, Having fun and spending time together with family and friends are key aspects of this task.

fields.title: Build a shelter
fields.description:
The purpose of building a shelter is to create a shelter or place of temporary residence for people, animals or others in need. This includes choosing a location, developing a construction plan, providing comfortable living conditions, creating infrastructure, and organizing financing and management.
Building a shelter often has a humanitarian purpose and requires a multifaceted effort to ensure the safety and care of those in need.

fields.title: Fix a bug in the program
fields.description:
The task of fixing a bug in a program is to identify and eliminate errors in the program code or functionality. This process involves analyzing bug reports, reproducing the problem, extracting the source code, determining the cause of the bug, and fixing it. The goal is to ensure stable and correct operation of the program,
as well as improving user experience.

fields.name: Create your project
fields.description: The challenge of creating your own project involves developing and implementing a unique initiative or idea. Includes stages from concept and planning to execution and promotion. This requires defining the project's goals, selecting the necessary resources, developing a business plan (if applicable), programming (in the case of technical projects), and ultimately - careful management of the process to achieve the goals and implement the conceived idea.

fields.name: Project 2
fields.description:
The project aims to develop a smart assistant that will facilitate task management and increase productivity. Includes functionality for creating, editing and tracking tasks, notifications, time analysis and priorities.
The app also provides calendar integration and the ability to sync data between devices. The goal of the project is to provide users with an effective tool for managing their time and tasks.

fields.name: Buy a car
fields.description:
The 'Buy a car' task involves the process of selecting, purchasing and registering a car. The stages include identifying needs and preferences, market research, choosing the right car, conducting a test drive, identifying financial opportunities, completing the transaction and obtaining the necessary documents.
The goal of the task is to successfully purchase a vehicle that meets the requirements and provides satisfaction of ownership.
